A yellow rectangular block (index 9) sits atop the two green blocks. An orange triangular block (presumably index 16) sits on top, completing the structure.

**3. Determine the Assembly Order:**

The assembly order needs to be inferred carefully to ensure structural stability. A bottom-up approach is most logical:

```json
{
```
